#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:2
msgid "焊盘沾胶检测（Glue on Pad）"
msgstr "Glue on Pad Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:6
msgid "检测焊盘上是否存在点胶 / 残胶等，通过颜色比例判定。"
msgstr ""
"Detects glue dots or residual glue on the solder pad, using a color-ratio "
"decision."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the tool's "
"parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:-1
msgid "模板编辑器中的焊盘沾胶检测元件示例"
msgstr "Example of a Glue-on-Pad inspection component in the Template Editor"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/glue_on_pad.rst:18
msgid "**有效比例范围（Valid Ratio Ranges）**：胶体颜色范围对应的有效比例区间。"
msgstr "**Valid Ratio Ranges**: the OK ratio band for the glue color range."
